des: Listen to the Maryland Fishing Report from the Maryland Department of Natural Resources for the latest hotspots, catch of the week, fishing conditions and more. You can request specific information for the upper, middle or lower Chesapeake Bay, freshwater fishing or Atlantic Ocean and coastal bays. Simply say ‘Alexa, open Maryland Fishing Report.’ Be in the know before you go!
